column5: If anyone is familiar with the black river road area I have a question about a particular back lake, I've fished most back lakes in the area and done tons if hunting in the area, but one lake eludes me. Just want to see if anyone has camped on it. Thanks, R
Can't help ya if we don't know the name of the lake. I know the area fairly well, but I go in there off #35, not off 118. More the northern end of all that land in there.  PM me if you want....  S.
In the process,  my son feed a bag of roe i defrosted to the dogs about an hour ago. Wonder if he's mad he's not going lol.
Thanks, I'll send you a PM, just don't want to ruin anyones honey hole.
I only fish there in the winter..way easier to get into allot of those lakes on a sled.
